### 1. Teste de Cadastro (Register)
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Pedro Alves de Paula",
  "email": "pedro@teste.com",
  "password": "UmaSenhaParaTeste$%132"
}

### 2. Teste de Login (Recebendo o JWT)
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "pedro@teste.com",
  "password": "UmaSenhaParaTeste$%132"
}

### 3. Teste do ValidationPipe (Forçando um erro de propósito)
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Teste de Erro",
  "email": "email_invalido_sem_arroba"
}
### ==========================================
### VARIÁVEIS GLOBAIS
### Dica: O REST Client permite criar variáveis para não precisar copiar e colar IDs
### ==========================================
# @baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
# @token = cole_o_seu_token_jwt_aqui
# @adminToken = cole_o_token_do_admin_aqui

@catalogItemId = cole_um_id_do_catalogo_aqui
@addressId = cole_um_id_de_endereco_aqui
@appointmentId = cole_um_id_de_agendamento_aqui

### ==========================================
### 1. AUTENTICAÇÃO (Auth)
### ==========================================

### Registrar Cliente
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Cliente Teste",
  "email": "cliente@teste.com",
  "password": "senha-segura-123"
}

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "cliente@teste.com",
  "password": "senha-segura-123"
}


### ==========================================
### 2. CATÁLOGO DE SERVIÇOS (Catalog)
### ==========================================

### Criar Serviço (Somente ADMIN)
POST {{baseUrl}}/catalog
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Corte Degradê",
  "description": "Corte na máquina com disfarce navalhado",
  "price": 35.00,
  "durationMinutes": 40
}

### Listar Catálogo (Público)
GET {{baseUrl}}/catalog

### Atualizar Serviço (Somente ADMIN)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/catalog/{{catalogItemId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 40.00
}


### ==========================================
### 3. ENDEREÇOS DO CLIENTE (Address)
### ==========================================

### Adicionar Endereço
POST {{baseUrl}}/addresses
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "street": "Rua das Flores",
  "number": "123",
  "complement": "Apto 42",
  "neighborhood": "Centro",
  "city": "João Monlevade",
  "state": "MG",
  "zipCode": "35930-000"
}

### Listar Meus Endereços
GET {{baseUrl}}/addresses
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ==========================================
### 4. AGENDAMENTOS (Appointment)
### ==========================================

### Criar Agendamento (O cliente agenda um serviço do catálogo)
POST {{baseUrl}}/appointments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "scheduledAt": "2026-06-25T14:30:00Z",
  "catalogItemId": "{{catalogItemId}}",
  "addressId": "{{addressId}}" 
}

### Listar Meus Agendamentos (O cliente vê o próprio histórico)
GET {{baseUrl}}/appointments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Atualizar Status do Agendamento (Somente ADMIN confirma ou cancela)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/appointments/{{appointmentId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "CONFIRMED"
}